newsTitle: Official Statements on the Senate Resolution #28 & Draft Subtitute Bill Amending CA #146
newsCaption: FICTAP has released two official statements containing initial comments from the National Chairperson, Estrellita 'Neng' Juliano-Tamano regarding the Senate Resolution #28 & Draft Subtitute Bill Amending CA #146.
newsBody: FICTAP has released two official statements containing initial comments from the National Chairperson, Estrellita 'Neng' Juliano-Tamano regarding the Senate Resolution #28 & Draft Subtitute Bill Amending CA #146.
